            "title": "滬指開市跌27點 深成指跌114點再失守萬四關",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市初段回吐，上證綜指以3967點開市，跌27點或0.69%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市報13928點，亦跌114點或0.81%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數跌32點或0.72%，開報4562點；創業板指數開市報3316點，跌31點或0.94%。</p>\n</div>",
