        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段略回 恒指跌136點報25756點 阿里巴巴低開2.69%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股開市初段跟隨日韓股市略為回吐，恒生指數開市報25756點，跌136點或0.53%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數開報4868點，跌54點或1.11%；國企指數以8623點開市，跌53點或0.62%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股互有升跌，滙控(00005)開報138.8元，升0.14%；友邦(01299)開報88.15元，跌0.56%。阿里巴巴(09988)開報123.1元，跌2.69%；騰訊(00700)開報506.5元，跌0.3%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">領展(00823)以溢價售新加坡零售物業，該股今早開報37.8元，升0.27%。聯想控股(03396)以逾27億元人民幣出售所持東航物流(601156.SH)股份，該股今早開報9.06元，升0.56%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">多家公司為今年首季業績發盈喜，股價今早在競價時段個別發展。中國鋁業(02600)開報12.4元，暫時無升跌；中偉新材(02579)開報36.48元，升0.33%；廣合科技(01989)則跌0.82%，以120元開市。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15850357-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e7%95%a5%e5%9b%9e-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c136%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125756%e9%bb%9e-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e5%b7%b4%e5%b7%b4%e4%bd%8e%e9%96%8b2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 09:25:52",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
